FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783945154
OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,FThe sell-out concert also became the
OL,8,Fhighest attended BST Hyde Park gig
OL,9,Fwith a crowd of 69,999, after the day
OL,10,Ffestival series increased its capacity
OL,11,Fthis year.
OL,13,FSpeaking before his certificate was
OL,14,Fpresented, Pitbull said: "Record
OL,15,Fbreaking, record making, history in
OL,16,Fthe making.
OL,18,F"Thank you London, thank you to the
OL,19,Ffans, thank you Hyde Park, thank you
OL,20,Fto the Bald-es."
OL,26,@vD@ZOUzD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
