OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783945154
OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,FMr Worldwide, real name Armando
OL,8,FChristian Perez, was presented with
OL,9,Fthe framed Guinness World Record
OL,10,Fcertificate by Greg James after the
OL,11,FBBC Radio 1 presenter came up with the
OL,12,Fidea earlier this year and texted the
OL,13,Fsinger on air.
OL,15,FAfter an official from the Guinness
OL,16,FWorld Records announced the number,
OL,17,FPitbull shouted, "We did it Bald-es,
OL,18,Fwe did it Bald-es."
OL,26,@yD@ROUzD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783945154
OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,FAsked how he felt, the musician said:
OL,8,F"Tell you what I'm speechless at this
OL,9,Fpoint but I can tell you this much, I
OL,10,Fsay it to the Bald-es all the time in
OL,11,Fthe shows, when y'all put on them bald
OL,12,Fcaps you know you're about to have the
OL,13,Ftime of your life and now you're
OL,14,Fofficially in the Guinness book of
OL,15,FWorld Records."
OL,17,FPitbull set the record as the first
OL,18,Fperson to attempt the feat under
OL,19,Fofficial adjudication, meaning there
OL,20,Fwas no previous record to beat.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
