PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783945154
OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,FHe continued: "It's a blessing. It's
OL,8,Fan honour.
OL,10,F"First of all, to all the Bald-es and
OL,11,Fall the fans out there, what an
OL,12,Fhonour, a blessing, and it's still
OL,13,Famazing to go around any city.
OL,15,F"See, there's nowhere I can hide at
OL,16,Fthis point anywhere in the world,
OL,17,Fbecause you know when I'm in your city
OL,18,Fat this point.
OL,26,@oD@OOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783945154
OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,F"So to all the Bald-es, without y'all,
OL,8,Flike I said before, there's no
OL,9,FPitbull, no movement, no revolution.
OL,11,F"But man, way to represent and who
OL,12,Fwould ever thought a first-generation
OL,13,FCuban would be able to be in London,
OL,14,Frecord breaking and record making."
OL,16,FPitbull fans, known as Bald-es, rushed
OL,17,Fto the main stage in their bald caps
OL,18,Fat the festival in order to be counted
OL,19,Fas temperatures were forecast to hit
OL,20,F31C in the capital.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@cOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
