OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783945154
OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,FMany sported the singer's signature
OL,8,Fblack aviators and stick on black
OL,9,Fgoatees, juggling pints of drink as
OL,10,Fthey carried inflatable globes.
OL,12,FAs the count began, James told the
OL,13,Fcrowd: "Quickly though, are there any
OL,14,Factual bald people here?
OL,16,F"You do need, sir, you do need a bald
OL,17,Fcap on your bald head for this to
OL,18,Fcount. You will not be counted.
OL,26,@uD@HOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783945154
OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,F"I know you're bald and I know you've
OL,8,Fgone through a lot, but this won't
OL,9,Fcount."
OL,11,FTowards the end of the show, Pitbull
OL,12,Fled the crowd on a singalong of
OL,13,FOasis's Wonderwall, which he said was
OL,14,Fhis way of thanking fans for helping
OL,15,Fhim set the record, while fans flung
OL,16,Ftheir bald caps in the air as
OL,17,Ffireworks exploded over the stage
OL,18,Fduring Give Me Everything, the final
OL,19,Fsong.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
