OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,FIt comes after fans began a trend of
OL,8,Fattending Pitbull's concerts dressing
OL,9,Fup as him, sporting suits, aviator
OL,10,Fglasses and bald caps.
OL,12,FThe trend has gone viral in recent
OL,13,Fyears, with videos of audience-packed
OL,14,Farenas full of bald cap wearing fans
OL,15,Fsinging his songs back at him.
OL,17,FPrior to Friday's gig, the singer and
OL,18,Ffestival organisers had appealed for
OL,19,Fvolunteers to count bald caps in the
OL,20,Fcrowd.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
