OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,FSupermarket chain Aldi also supplied
OL,8,F300 caps to Mr Worldwide fans outside
OL,9,Fthe London park and temporarily
OL,10,Frebranded itself as "Baldi".
OL,12,FThe rapper is among the roster of all-
OL,13,Fmale main stage headliners performing
OL,14,Fat the festival this year, following
OL,15,Fon from shows by US band Maroon 5,
OL,16,Ffolk pop group Mumford And Sons and an
OL,17,Fupcoming set from Scottish singer
OL,18,FLewis Capaldi.
OL,26,@rD@UOUrD@[O]
