OL,3,CMr World Record: Pitbull recognised
OL,4,Cfor largest gathering of people in
OL,5,Cbald caps
OL,7,FMiami-born Pitbull is best known for
OL,8,Fthe songs Fireball, Timber, Time Of
OL,9,FOur Lives, On The Floor, Give Me
OL,10,FEverything, Feel This Moment and Don't
OL,11,FStop The Party.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/11
